{"tid":2303704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國突稱不丹東部野生保護區是中方「領土」　又在西南部有爭議地區建村派人入住","createTime":"2020-11-28T07:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T07:36:48.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e361e60759c8107b8b1b5ce1b6b5e27ea8696b07","tid":2303704,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uzdE__QmOmk_oQMDyw2A97hogrg=/497x635/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TKFNG5UXQJFDDJDFRUG6B35Q5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuzdE__QmOmk_oQMDyw2A97hogrg%3D%2F497x635%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTKFNG5UXQJFDDJDFRUG6B35Q5Y.jpg&h=f54dde5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中方興建龐達村的情況。上圖為去年12月，下圖為今年10月。 互聯網<br />\n...<br />\n中國再與鄰國發生邊境糾紛，最新衞星照片顯示，中國在與不丹存在主權爭議的邊境地區興建村落，早前又突然聲稱不丹東部一片約740平方公里的野生動物保護區是中國領土，並阻擋國際組織向不丹資助區內項目，聲稱因為該地區存「主權爭議」。<br />\n<br />\n新村落名為「龐達村」，位於不丹西南部與中方接壤邊境附近，中不在該地區的主權爭議仍未解決。衞星影像顯示中方去年已開始興建房屋，並在今年10月前完成，村落亦設有道路和軍事碉堡。《紐約時報》形容中方對建立新村落直認不諱，10月18日更在村內舉行揭幕儀式，邀請中國上海市委副書記于紹良出席。<br />\n<br />\n麻省理工大學政治系教授傅泰林（Taylor Fravel）表示，當中國已在區內設立一定規模的基建，便更不願意退出該區，相信中方1990年代提出與不丹的妥協方案將無法再實現。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201128/63VPTMMV2JEFDD57VYIQOF2WEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201128%2F63VPTMMV2JEFDD57VYIQOF2WEI%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CjIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=6be5341b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201128%2F63VPTMMV2JEFDD57VYIQOF2WEI%2F&h=e75c8b47\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201128/63VPTMMV2JEFDD57VYIQOF2WEI/</a>"},{"pid":"479d5b941626c2221864a1e9d8833232992148db","tid":2303704,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:20:40.000Z","msg":"仆街支那屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbbf9a2526d5b268c65787589edaeac2881ade4","tid":2303704,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:36:48.000Z","msg":"弱國注定玩完中國由佢未出世前幾千年開始借D二食人D地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}